l which microorganisms are in my explorer samplewe use s ribosomal rna s rrna gene sequencing on an illumina next generation sequencer to find out which kinds of bacteria and other microorganisms are in your gut based on a ribosomal gene present in microbial dna s s rrna gene sequencing enables us to classify microbes all the way down to the genus andor species level while filtering out any genetic material from humans and other organismsthis is the same sequencing method used in the majority of microbiome studies in this area so it gives us the greatest ability to compare with other studies making your data more relevantwhat if i’m having issues registering or activating my explorer collection kityou might need to update your version of chrome firefox or safari if you are still having issues email supportubiomecom and we will do our best to helpwhat if i’ve damaged or contaminated my sample or sample tubenot to worry your kit includes a replacement sample tube and a second swab just in case you need it if you need additional replacement items just email supportubiomecom and we will send you what you need or replace your kit as soon as possiblehow can i contact you by telephoneemail is actually the fastest way to get answers to your questions our expert support team supportubiomecom will respond to your query within  hoursdo you ship outside the united statesyes we accept payment through major credit cards and will ship to almost every country in the world our kits comply with all iata regulations for exempt samples and sending and receiving your samples should not be a problem you can return your sample via regular mail as it is shelfstable for over a month there is an additional  shipping charge for international nonus orderswhen can i expect my kit to arrivestandard shipping on domestic orders will deliver your kit within  business days for international orders delivery can sometimes take several weeks if you need your kits more quickly please make sure to select