ther sites include additional tubes and swabs you probably did get everything you need but in case you didnt or if you arent sure just send us an email at supportubiomecomi knocked over a tubemy dog chewed my swabsi contaminated my sampleour kits come with a spare tube and swab so any mistake can be remedied by using the spare included if you should still need a replacement just email at supportubiomecom and well send you a replacement immediatelyhow do i collect my sampleall instructions for the kit you ordered are available online once you activate your kit please go to appubiomecom and follow the instructions there youll find out interesting tidbits like how long to swab for and what to do with your sample before sending it back to us we also made a handy little video for you about sampling your skin microbiome you can watch it hereif youre having trouble locating the instructions theyve been transcribed in full below startsampling takes less than  min per site faster than a dividing bacteriawe recommend you leave your kit on your bathroom counter so its ready first thing in the morningsample first thing in the morning before you brush your teeth or eat breakfast sampleopen the tube you want to sample and the follow the sitespecific instructions belowgutswab your used toilet paper to collect a tiny amount of poopnote  this probably way less than you think you need  just enough to change the color of the swabmouthvigorously rub the swab across the inside of each cheek for  secondsnote  do not touch your teeth or gums to the swabskin wet the swab with the pcr water included in your kit do not use regular waterswab along the lower half of the crease behind your ear for  minutenote  pull your ear forward with one hand and pull your hair out of the way if necessarynose wet the swab with the pcr water included in your kit do not use regular waterswab around the inside of each nostril at the depth of the cotton on the swab for  seconds eachmale genitalswet the swab with the pcr water included in your kit do not use regular waterswab in a circular motion around the base of the head of the penis for one minute where the head of the penis intersects the shaftnote  if your penis is uncircumcised pull back your foreskin firstfemale genitalswet the swab with the pcr water included in your kit do not use regular watersquat slightly and insert the swab as far as possible while still comfortable into the vagina swish it around for one minute to collect your samplenote  spread your labia with one hand and use the other to swab stir and shakeput the used swab into the vial and stir it for  minute to transfer the bacteriadiscard the swab in the trashclose the tube tightly and shake vigorously for  minute sendall of kits include a secure mailer so that you can send your samples right back to usus kits come with prepaid postage just drop the envelope in the mailwill my gut sample smellno the amount of the sample needed is quite small and the cotton swab goes immediately into the lysing solution in a closed container nothing smelly at allwhat kind of results will i getafter your sample has been analyzed you get to be an explorer and learn about the vast rainforest of bacteria in your body logging in to ubiomecom youll see detailed information on each of these bacteria  what their names are how many of each kind there are what their functions are in the body you may find yourself curious to compare your results with the aggregate results of everyone whos done the test and with specific groups of people say you want to look at how your microbiome compares to vegans or smokers or people on antibiotics you can do thatit’s important to be aware that ubiome is designed to be a tool for personal research not a diagnostic tool you wont find any predictions about your future health and your results will not diagnose any medical conditionwhat you will find is a chance to better understand your microbiome how you compare to others and even how you compare to yourself over time before and after going glutenfree or starting a new medication for example last but not least you may find a warm glow in your heart from knowing that you are contributing to advancements in research that may have tremendous benefit for the future of human health and wellbeingwill i be able to download my raw dataabsolutely from your samples dashboard you will have the opportunity to click either download taxonomy csv or “download taxonomy json” or “download sequence data” from the advanced tabtaxonomy files are a summary of all the microbes we found in your sample which you can see either as a spreadsheet csv or in an easy machinereadable form json suitable for analysis in a programming language like python the taxonomy includes details about the specific microbes their taxonomic rank the percentage abundance in the sample and more  sequence data is the complete raw fastq files downloaded directly from our highspeed gene sequencing machinefor a more complete tutorial on what to do with your raw data read richard spragues article on our blogwhat is the difference between ubiome explorer™ and smartgut™ubiome explorer™ is a citizen science tool to explore the microbiome of the nose mouth skin gut and genitals and to track changes in the microbiome it includes online interactive tools to help you understand how your bacteria compare to others and yourself over time smartgut is a clinical laboratory test ordered by healthcare providers for patients with chronic gut conditions it detects  bacterial targets at a high level of accuracy to better understand  if there are specific pathogens present that might be causing illness  the balance of commensal and beneficial bacteria that may be contributing to your symptoms and  risk factors relating to the microbiomesmartgut™ vs explorer™ infographicwhat is ubiomehow are you involving the public in your workdoes the ubiome research study have institutional review board approvalhow do you ensure the privacy of user data and resultsdoes ubiome collaborate on a research and citizen scientist studieshow do i get the latest ubiome newswhat is ubiomeubiome is the leading microbial genomics company providing stateoftheart dna sequencing to healthcare patients and citizen scientists we aim to advance the science of microbial genomics and provide everyday people with vital information that enables them to take greater control over their health and their lives our technology based on research pioneered by the national institutes for health nih human microbiome project has enabled tens of thousand of citizen scientists and collaborating institutions to participate in largescale microbiome studieshow are you involving the public in your workwe are involving the public in data collection hypothesisgeneration and hypothesis testing with our explorer collection kits and the ubiome explorer our goal is to build a community around longterm sequencing of the human microbiome your smartgut™ sample and data will not be used for research and development unless you allow us to do so by signing the consent when registering your smartgut™ sampledoes the ubiome research study have institutional review board approvalyes an institutional review board irb is a committee that approves oversees and reviews biomedical and behavioral research involving humans the committee determines whether or not research should be done and advocates for the individual participantubiome has received research study approval from asentral inc if you choose to participate in our research study for smartgut™ you will need to read and sign our electronic informed consent form that outlines the risks and benefits of participation we are committed to caring ethically for everyone in our communityhow do you ensure the privacy of user data and resultsyour privacy is our top priority to ensure the privacy of your data and your results we use multiple layers of encryption the highest levels of computer security and follow strict hipaa protocols you control your data and can choose whether or not you consent to having your data be anonymized and aggregated into our ubiome research studiesdoes ubiome collaborate on a research and citizen scientist studiesour goal is to build a community around longterm sequencing of the human microbiome we want to engage and involve you in the process please contact us at studiesubiomecomhow do i get the latest ubiome newsto keep up with ubiome and the latest developments in the world of microbial genomics visit our blog or follow us on twitter and facebook or you can subscribe to our weekly enewsletter belowemail addressthank you please check your email to confirm your subscriptionoops something went wrong while submitting the form  ubiome inccareersabout ubiomepartnersnews  presscontact usrefer a friendread the ubiome blogmeet the microbiomeprivacy policyterms of servicenotice of privacy practicesresearch consentscontact usread the ubiome blog  ubiome inc microsoft personalized ad preferences to opt out of personalized ads in this browser your browser history must allow firstparty and thirdparty cookies and you must have your browsing experience set to not delete browsing history on exit instructions for enabling cookies and configuring your browsing history may be available in your browsers settings privacy or help documentation sign in hold on… we’re sorry but this didn’t work you can’t turn off personalized ads right now because your browser is currently blocking thirdparty cookies we can help you fix this issue let’s get started depending on what browser you use open options or settings make sure that thirdparty cookies are not blocked anymore to find out how search your browser’s help revisit httpchoicemicrosoftcomoptout and then on the “personalized ads in this browser” tile click off ext about our ads to create a more customized online experience some of the ads you may receive on microsoft websites and apps are tailored to your previous activiti