plorer to learn more about your microbiomeget sequencedxactionable insights to improve your gut healthubiome’s smartgut™ is the worlds first sequencingbased clinical microbiome screening test providing detailed and accurate information to help you understand your gut healthlearn moreexplore your microbiomebe a citizen scientist with the ubiome explorer™ you can help advance science discover the bacteria that live in and on your body and learn how diet and lifestyle factors affect your microbiomeexploreabout the smartgut™ testsmartgut is the first sequencingbased clinical microbiome screening test the test detects beneficial and pathogenic microorganisms associated with specific infections lifestyle choices and gut conditions including inflammatory bowel disease ibd and irritable bowel syndrome ibsusing advanced dna sequencing technology smartgut detects pathogens and beneficial microorganisms that might affect your healthwith smartgut you and your doctor can gain valuable insights to better understand what’s going on inside your gut and then take steps to feel bettersimple collection kityour smartgut test includes an easytouse collection kit that you can use in the comfort and privacy of your own home once you collect your sample simply mail it back to our lab for processingdetailed test reportyou will receive a detailed report with information on microorganisms associated with lifestyle choices specific infections and gut conditions you and your doctor can use this report to gain valuable insight into your gut health that might help to determine a diagnosishow to request smartgut™fill out your information and request a test below once we receive doctor’s approval you will receive your collection kit in the mail within a few business daysrequest your testdoctor orders testtest kit shippedsample at homereturn your samplewhen you have your kit follow the instructions inside the box to collect and return your samplerequest your testcostsmartgut is fully or partially covered by most health insurance companies under outofnetwork healthcare benefitsif you have additional questions please contact our billing specialist teamcontact a billing specialistour social missionfor peoplewe are committed to empowering people to better understand and take greater control over their health through our ubiome explorer kits and our smartgut test we give people access to tools to better understand the microbiome and healthfor scienceto advance the science of the microbiome we work with more than  researchers from around the world at institutions such as harvard stanford ucsf national university of singapore and university college londonfor the worldour projects include large scale citizen scientist studies partnerships with researchers and organizations and support for underfunded scientific discovery via our  million microbiome impact grant initiative as part of the white house national microbiome initiative  ubiome inccareersabout ubiomepartnersnews  presscontact usrefer a friendread the ubiome blogmeet the microbiomeprivacy policyterms of servicenotice of privacy practicesresearch consentscontact usread the ubiome blog  ubiome inc ubiome ubiome